{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "自动排产系统 API",
    "summary": "自动排产系统后端接口文档",
    "description": "\n## 接口文档说明\n\n这是自动排产系统的后端 Swagger / OpenAPI 文档页，用于查看、联调和验证当前后端接口。\n\n### 返回结构约定\n\n- 大多数 JSON 接口统一返回：`{ code, message, data }`\n- `code = 0` 表示成功\n- 文件导出接口直接返回二进制文件流，不走 JSON 包装\n\n### 受保护接口认证\n\n以下接口默认需要先通过 `/api/auth/login` 完成账号密码登录，并携带会话 Cookie：\n\n- `/api/admin/*`\n- `/api/data/*`\n- `/api/exports/*`\n\n### Cookie 联调步骤\n\n1. 调用 `POST /api/auth/login`，传入登录账号和登录密码\n2. 确认响应头 `Set-Cookie` 已写入用户会话 Cookie\n3. 使用同一浏览器会话或同一个 Cookie Jar 继续调用受保护接口\n4. 可通过 `GET /api/auth/session` 检查当前会话状态\n5. 联调结束后调用 `POST /api/auth/logout` 注销会话\n\n### 非浏览器客户端说明\n\n- Postman、curl、脚本联调时，需要先调登录接口保存 Cookie\n- 后续请求继续携带该 Cookie；不能再只传旧版管理员令牌\n\n### 入参阅读方式\n\n- `Authorize` / `Security`：表示认证信息（如用户会话 Cookie）\n- `Parameters`：表示路径参数、查询参数、Cookie 参数\n- `Request body`：表示 JSON 请求体\n- 每个接口说明中还会按“认证信息 / 路径参数 / 查询参数 / 请求体”再做一层结构化整理\n\n### 推荐使用方式\n\n1. 先在本页确认接口路径、请求参数和请求体结构\n2. 联调前优先对照前端页面实际调用的接口\n3. 发生数据状态异常时，优先查看同步、排产和 snapshot 相关接口\n",
    "version": "0.1.0"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/health": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "Health",
        "operationId": "health_health_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {}
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "Health。\n\n### 接口结构\n#### 响应结构\n- `200`：Successful Response"
      }
    },
    "/api/schedules/options/product-series": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "排产查询"
        ],
        "summary": "获取产品系列筛选项",
        "operationId": "get_product_series_options_api_schedules_options_product_series_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "标准成功响应，返回结构为 `ApiResponse_list_str__`。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse_list_str__"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "获取产品系列筛选项。\n\n### 接口结构\n#### 响应结构\n- `200`：标准成功响应，返回结构为 `ApiResponse_list_str__`。"
      }
    },
    "/api/dashboard/overview": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "排产查询"
        ],
        "summary": "获取排产总览",
        "description": "返回整机排产、零件排产、时间窗口统计和交付风险订单等总览信息，供 Dashboard 页面展示。\n\n### 接口结构\n#### 响应结构\n- `200`：标准成功响应，外层为 `ApiResponse_DashboardOverviewResponse_`，其中 `data` 字段为 `DashboardOverviewResponse`。",
        "operationId": "get_dashboard_overview_api_dashboard_overview_get",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "标准成功响应，外层为 `ApiResponse_DashboardOverviewResponse_`，其中 `data` 字段为 `DashboardOverviewResponse`。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse_DashboardOverviewResponse_"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/schedules": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "排产查询"
        ],
        "summary": "查询整机排产列表",
        "description": "按合同号、客户、机型、排产状态、预警等级和日期范围等条件分页查询整机排产列表。\n\n### 接口结构\n#### 查询参数\n- `page_no`（可选）：分页页码，从 1 开始。\n- `page_size`（可选）：每页返回的记录数。\n- `contract_no`（可选）：合同号；支持精确匹配或关键字筛选。\n- `customer_name`（可选）：客户名称；支持关键字筛选。\n- `product_series`（可选）：产品系列筛选值。\n- `product_model`（可选）：机型筛选值。\n- `plant`（可选）：工厂编码筛选值；用于区分同物料在不同工厂下的 BOM、快照、查询与导出结果。\n- `order_no`（可选）：销售订单号筛选值。\n- `schedule_status`（可选）：排产状态筛选值。\n- `schedule_bucket`（可选）：排产桶筛选；如 unscheduled（未排产）、risk（风险订单）。\n- `warning_level`（可选）：预警等级筛选值。\n- `drawing_released`（可选）：是否已发图；true 表示已发图，false 表示未发图。\n- `date_from`（可选）：日期范围开始值，格式通常为 yyyy-MM-dd。\n- `date_to`（可选）：日期范围结束值，格式通常为 yyyy-MM-dd。\n- `sort_field`（可选）：排序字段名；可选字段请参考接口说明或前端筛选项。\n- `sort_order`（可选）：排序方向；通常为 asc（升序）或 desc（降序）。\n\n#### 响应结构\n- `200`：标准成功响应，外层为 `ApiResponse_PageResult_ScheduleListItem__`，其中 `data` 字段为 `PageResult_ScheduleListItem_`。\n- `422`：请求参数或请求体校验失败。",
        "operationId": "list_schedules_api_schedules_get",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "page_no",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "minimum": 1,
              "default": 1,
              "title": "Page No"
            },
            "description": "分页页码，从 1 开始。"
          },
          {
            "name": "page_size",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "maximum": 100,
              "minimum": 1,
              "default": 20,
              "title": "Page Size"
            },
            "description": "每页返回的记录数。"
          },
          {
            "name": "contract_no",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Contract No"
            },
            "description": "合同号；支持精确匹配或关键字筛选。"
          },
          {
            "name": "customer_name",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Customer Name"
            },
            "description": "客户名称；支持关键字筛选。"
          },
          {
            "name": "product_series",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Product Series"
            },
            "description": "产品系列筛选值。"
          },
          {
            "name": "product_model",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Product Model"
            },
            "description": "机型筛选值。"
          },
          {
            "name": "plant",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Plant"
            },
            "description": "工厂编码筛选值；用于区分同物料在不同工厂下的 BOM、快照、查询与导出结果。"
          },
          {
            "name": "order_no",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Order No"
            },
            "description": "销售订单号筛选值。"
          },
          {
            "name": "schedule_status",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Schedule Status"
            },
            "description": "排产状态筛选值。"
          },
          {
            "name": "schedule_bucket",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string",
                  "pattern": "^(unscheduled|risk)$"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Schedule Bucket"
            },
            "description": "排产桶筛选；如 unscheduled（未排产）、risk（风险订单）。"
          },
          {
            "name": "warning_level",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Warning Level"
            },
            "description": "预警等级筛选值。"
          },
          {
            "name": "drawing_released",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "boolean"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Drawing Released"
            },
            "description": "是否已发图；true 表示已发图，false 表示未发图。"
          },
          {
            "name": "date_from",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Date From"
            },
            "description": "日期范围开始值，格式通常为 yyyy-MM-dd。"
          },
          {
            "name": "date_to",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Date To"
            },
            "description": "日期范围结束值，格式通常为 yyyy-MM-dd。"
          },
          {
            "name": "sort_field",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Sort Field"
            },
            "description": "排序字段名；可选字段请参考接口说明或前端筛选项。"
          },
          {
            "name": "sort_order",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                {
                  "type": "null"
                }
              ],
              "title": "Sort Order"
            },
            "description": "排序方向；通常为 asc（升序）或 desc（降序）。"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "标准成功响应，外层为 `ApiResponse_PageResult_ScheduleListItem__`，其中 `data` 字段为 `PageResult_ScheduleListItem_`。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse_PageResult_ScheduleListItem__"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 0,
                  "message": "success",
                  "data": {
                    "total": 1,
                    "page_no": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "items": [
                      {
                        "order_line_id": 101,
                        "contract_no": "HT20260323001",
                        "customer_name": "江苏某客户",
                        "product_series": "X7",
                        "product_model": "X7-500",
                        "order_no": "SO20260323001",
                        "quantity": 1,
                        "confirmed_delivery_date": "2026-03-30T00:00:00",
                        "planned_start_date": "2026-03-24T00:00:00",
                        "planned_end_date": "2026-03-28T00:00:00",
                        "warning_level": "normal",
                        "schedule_status": "scheduled"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "请求参数或请求体校验失败。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                },
                "example": {
                  "detail": [
                    {
                      "loc": [
                        "body",
                        "order_line_ids"
                      ],
                      "msg": "Field required",
                      "type": "missing"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/part-schedules": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
